      <p><em>PHP 85,270 / mo</em></p>
      <ul style="text-align:left; margin: 0 auto 10px; max-width: 320px;">
        <li>Engine: Hybrid, 4-cylinder, In-Line, 16-valve DOHC, Chain Drive (with Dual VWT-i)</li>
